title: Ep 2614 - Saving Gada Electronics
shortDesc: Jethalal is pestered by inquiries about the sale of his shop. Jethalal decides to call up Taarak Mehta to find a solution to his problem but Taarak Mehta is out of the city.

title: Ep 2615 - Popatlal to the Rescue
shortDesc: Jethalal reaches Gokuldham society and faces one question after the other about the sale of Gada Electronics. Then, Popatlal makes a heroic entry and informs Jethalal that he has found a solution for his problem.

title: Ep 2616 - Beware of Surma Bhai
shortDesc: Popatlal has got the contact of Surma Bhai’s sister, Kajal. Jethalal is overjoyed thinking that his problem is solved but after calling Kajal, Jethalal finds his problem getting more complicated.

title: Ep 2617 - On The Way
shortDesc: All the men decide to meet Surma Bhai and talk him out of buying Gada Electronics so all of them leave to meet Surma Bhai at his farmhouse in Madh Island at the given time.

title: Ep 2618 - The Widow On The Road
shortDesc: While all the men are on their way to Surma Bhai's farmhouse in Madh Island, they encounter a widow wearing a white saree in the middle of the road who offers them something.

title: Ep 2619 - The Negotiation
shortDesc: Jethalal and the other men of Gokuldham society reach Surma Bhai's farmhouse and meet him. Jethalal explains to him the entire situation involving the misunderstanding between him and Bagha and Nattu Kaka

title: Ep 2620 - All Hope is Gone
shortDesc: The negotiations between Jethalal and Surma Bhai fails. Surma Bhai reveals that he is buying Gada Electronics as a gift for his beloved brother-in-law., and will not under any circumstances withdraw the deal.

title: Ep 2621 - Consulting a Lawyer
shortDesc: Champaklal is furious after hearing that Surma Bhai will not negotiate under any circumstances. Dr. Hathi offers a solution and informs the society members to consult lawyer Dawawala.

title: Ep 2622 - The Last Resort
shortDesc: As a last resort, Jethalal decides to consult a lawyer about the entire situation revolving around Gada Electronics and Surma Bhai. Surma Bhai sends his men to Gokuldham Society to give Jethalal the final pay-cheque.

title: Ep 2623 - The Brainstorming
shortDesc: The Lawyer that Jethalal consulted advised him to file a case against Nattu Kaka and fire him from the job in order to make his case strong in front of Surma Bhai in the court but Jethalal refuses to do so.

title: Ep 2624 - All The Possibilities Are Exhausted
shortDesc: Jethalal and everyone else tries to think of a solution to save Gada Electronics from Surma Bhai and everyone come up with useless ideas and none that can actually help Jethalal.

title: Ep 2625 - Jethalal is Missing
shortDesc: Jethalal is heartbroken as he has no other choice other than selling Gada Electronics. Jethalal comes to the conclusion that he will bid adieu to his beloved shop and head back home. However, Jethalal never arrives at Gokuldham society.

title: Ep 2626 - Where Is Jethalal?
shortDesc: Jethalal is missing and everyone tries to calm Champaklal who waits for him to come back. Later Champaklal finds Jethalal sitting in society's temple complaining to God about his situation.

title: Ep 2627 - The Good News
shortDesc: After Surma finalizes the deal for Gada Electronics, the newspapers bring good news for Jethalaal and bad news for Surma. Surma is not happy about the news, whereas Gokuldham society celebrates the news.

title: Ep 2628 - The Tables are Turned
shortDesc: The ball is in Jethalal’s court as the tables are turned on Surma Bhai. Jethalal is escatic that the sale of Gada Electronics has been a blessing in disguise. Surma Bhai decides to con Nattu Kaka and Baga in order to cancel the deal.
